    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "To borrow @ellisonbg's beloved phrase---I think we are seeing a leaking in abstraction from having separate widget and output areas from the same input cell.  Perhaps it would be more clear to just have an input cell have output, which can be interspersed widgets and outputs.  The only objection I've heard is that the clear_output command is not well-defined, then.  So just make clear_output more explicit about exactly what it is clearing (or make it possible to clear _specific_ output instead of just a bazooka that clears everything.)\n"
  },
